    {%- comment -%}═══ TYPOGRAPHY ═══{%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="bg-section">
      <span class="bg-label">Typography</span>
      <h2>Type Scale</h2>
      <p>Headlines: <strong>Helvetica Rounded LT Pro</strong> (brand) → <strong>Nunito</strong> (web). Body: <strong>GT Pressura</strong> (brand) → <strong>Inter</strong> (web).</p>

      <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <div class="bg-type-row">
